description: BusyBox v1.7.2 (2017-11-13 17:29:07 CST) - A multi-functional toolbox providing simplified implementations of various Unix utilities. No directly related CVE vulnerabilities were found in the NVD.
GNU Wget 1.12 - File download utility with two known vulnerabilities: CVE-2009-3490 (certificate verification issue) and CVE-2010-2252 (filename spoofing vulnerability).
utelnetd - lightweight telnet server, no clear version information found.
